==English==
[[Category:English nouns]]
===Noun===
'''smith''' (''plural'' '''[[smiths]]''')

#A [[craftsperson]] who works [[metal]] into desired forms using a [[hammer]] and other tools, sometimes heating the metal to make it more [[workable]].


{{rfv-sense}}
#B Smith is a common last name that can also be used to refer to the female's [[vagina]] (adapted to go along with another common last name [[Johnson]] which refers to the male's [[penis]])


